It looks like there are a few issues with your email authentication setup ‚Äî I would be happy to help debug

It looks like you have two SPF records (one for google and one for registrar-servers), which violates the SPF spec and is likely what flagged your mail server for blacklisting.

You should consolidate those two SPF records into one:
"v=spf1 include:_spf.google.com include:spf.efwd.registrar-servers.com -all"
